OL,3,CLorry drivers may hold key to finding
OL,4,Cman in sexual assault, police say
OL,6,FPolice in Leicestershire are appealing
OL,7,Fto lorry drivers to come forward with
OL,8,Finformation relating to a sexual
OL,9,Fassault near Leicester Forest East
OL,10,Fservices on the M1 on Saturday.
OL,12,FA woman in her 20s was walking along
OL,13,FBaines Lane at around 6:45pm when she
OL,14,Fwas attacked, say police.
OL,16,FThe suspect then ran off towards the
OL,17,Fservice station after she shouted for
OL,18,Fhelp.
