OL,3,CLorry drivers may hold key to finding
OL,4,Cman in sexual assault, police say
OL,6,FHe is described as a white man in his
OL,7,F40s or 50s with a slim build, greying
OL,8,Fhair and a grey beard.
OL,10,FA spokesperson from Leicestershire
OL,11,FPolice said: "We believe the man may
OL,12,Fhave gone into the car park at the
OL,13,Fservices on the M1 southbound.
OL,15,F"I'm sure there'll have been people
OL,16,Fwho saw someone matching the
OL,17,Fdescription and I'd like to speak to
OL,18,Fanyone who can help.
OL,26,@sD@NOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
