OL,3,CLorry drivers may hold key to finding
OL,4,Cman in sexual assault, police say
OL,6,F"We know anyone using the services may
OL,7,Fhave travelled from outside
OL,8,FLeicestershire and I'm appealing for
OL,9,FHGV drivers and other drivers who
OL,10,Fstopped there between 5pm and 7pm to
OL,11,Fcome forward.
OL,13,F"I'd also be grateful to the public if
OL,14,Fthey are able to share our appeal for
OL,15,Finformation so it reaches those living
OL,16,Foutside our force area."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@XO]
